title: The Mummy - I Miss Films Like This
description: Some movies seem to improve with age, especially if everything else has gotten worse. The Mummy represents the kind of fun, escapist adventure that we just never seem to get anymore.

title: Star Trek - It's Dead, Jim
description: The news that Alex Kurtzman's contract to make Star Trek shows has been renewed by CBS for ANOTHER 5 years, is the final stake through the heart of this franchise. Star Trek is over, and it's not coming back.
